node.title: Murder hornets cause bees to make "fear screams"
node.description: The "fear scream"-like bee noise prompts colony members to gather and spread dung around the hive's entrance to repel the giant hornets.

node.title: Man escapes huge crocodile's jaws with pocketknife counterattack
node.description: The 64-year-old was fishing when the huge croc attacked him, but he fended the animal off with his knife, and "the odds of doing that are about zero."

node.title: Climate change conspiracies spreading rapidly during COP26
node.description: Amplified by bots and influencers, millions of posts on social media networks peddle false ideas about climate change.
